GS41tikaniku:4: TY_1.2ab/.mūrdhnā gaṇeśaṃ ca sarasvatīṃ ca salokapālaṃ parameśvaraṃ ca/
GS41tikaniku:5: TY_1.2cd/.padmodbhavaṃ padmadhanaṃ hariṃ ca trailokyadīpaṃ praṇamāmi bhānum//
GS41tikaniku:8: TY_1.4cd/.āyuṣi ca parijñāte śubham aśubhaṃ vā phalaṃ vācyam//
GS41tikaniku:10: TY_1.5cd/.janmasamayaṃ ca kecid vadanti na vadanti bahuvo 'nye//
GS41tikaniku:11: TY_1.6ab/.janmarkṣodayalagne tad api yayor vā yiyāsataḥ praśne/
GS41tikaniku:13: TY_1.7ab/.śatror horārāśis tad adhipatir janmabhaṃ tadīśo vā//
GS41tikaniku:14: TY_1.7cd/.yady aste hibuke vā tathāpi śatrur hato vācyaḥ//
GS41tikaniku:16: TY_1.8cd/.yadi cādareṇa pṛcchati daivajño nirdiśed vijayam//
GS41tikaniku:17: TY_1.9ab/.nandā bhadrā vijayā riktā pūrṇā ca nāmasadṛśaphalāḥ/
GS41tikaniku:18: TY_1.9cd/.nyūnasameṣṭā daśame tithayaḥ śukle kṛṣṇe pratīpās tāḥ//
GS41tikaniku:27: TY_1.14cd/.pūrveṣu triṣu yāmye pitrye ca vihāya madhyaniśam//
GS41tikaniku:28: TY_1.15ab/.na niśāpaścimabhāge punarvasau triṣu ca vaiṣṇavādyeṣu/
GS41tikaniku:30: TY_1.16ab/.prācyādi sapta sapta kramena dhiṣṇyāni kṛttikādīni/
GS41tikaniku:33: TY_1.17cd/.ājñām iva kuliśabhṛtaḥ patanti na cireṇa te vyasane//
GS41tikaniku:36: TY_1.19ab/.jyeṣṭhā prāgbhādrapadā rohiṇy athottarā ca phalgunyā/
GS41tikaniku:37: TY_1.19cd/.śūlāni prācyādiṣu teṣu gato 'tyeti yadi citram//
GS41tikaniku:45: TY_2.3cd/.saumye 'py anupacayasthe na bhavati yātrā śubhā yātuḥ//E3

GS41tikaniku:51: TY_3.4ab/.ahnaḥ pañcadaśāṃśo rātreś caivaṃ muhūrta iti saṃjñā/
GS41tikaniku:52: TY_3.4cd/.sa ca vijñeyas tajjñaiś chāyāyantrāmbubhir yuktyā//
GS41tikaniku:53: TY_3.5ab/.nakṣatravat kṣaṇānāṃ parighādi tadīśvaraiḥ samaṃ cintyam/
GS41tikaniku:54: TY_3.5cd/.phalam api tad eva dṛṣṭaṃ gargādyais tatra ca ślokāḥ//
GS41tikaniku:57: TY_3.7ab/.yaś cāṣṭamo muhūrto viriñcināmābhijit sa nirdiṣṭaḥ/
GS41tikaniku:67: TY_4.3ab/.sitapakṣādau candre śubhe śubhaṃ pakṣam aśubham aśubhe ca/
GS41tikaniku:68: TY_4.3cd/.kṛṣṇe gocaraśubhado na śubhaṃ pakṣa(kṣe) śubham atonyat//E3

GS41tikaniku:73: TY_5.3ab/.āye janmani rāśiṣu yeṣu śubhā bhāskaradvitīyai//
GS41tikaniku:94: TY_7.1ab/.lagnopagataiḥ saumyair ārogyaṃ bhavati cittasaukhyañ ca/
GS41tikaniku:96: TY_7.2ab/.vāhanasuhṛdāṃ vṛddhiś caturthagaiḥ pañcagaiś ca mantribalam/
GS41tikaniku:99: TY_7.3cd/.karmaṇi siddhir lābho balasampātaś ca daśamādyaiḥ//
GS41tikaniku:108: TY_7.8ab/.krūro 'py anukūlasthaḥ śasto lagne śubho 'pi vāniṣṭaḥ/
GS41tikaniku:109: TY_7.8cd/.vakrī na śubhaḥ kendre tadahas tadvargalagnañ ca//
GS41tikaniku:112: TY_7.10cd/.sūryādibhir anukūlais tad udayavargaiś ca tatsiddhiḥ//
GS41tikaniku:114: TY_7.11cd/.bhujagā iva mantrahatā bhavanty akāryakṣamā lagne//
GS41tikaniku:117: TY_7.12cd/.āyānti te svabhavanāni punaḥ kṛtārthāḥ dattā dvijātiṣu tathā vidhivad yathārthāḥ//
GS41tikaniku:118: TY_7.13ab/.ekasminn api kendre yadi saumyo na graho 'sti yātrāyām/
GS41tikaniku:119: TY_7.13cd/.janmany atha vā karmaṇi na tac chubhaṃ prāhur ācāryāḥ//
GS41tikaniku:122: TY_7.15ab/.yāyibhir anukūlasthair yānaṃ paurair vigṛhya cāsīnam/
GS41tikaniku:123: TY_7.15cd/.pauretarair api śubhair yāyād ardhena sainyasya//
GS41tikaniku:124: TY_7.16ab/.sarvair apy aśubhakaraiḥ śubhadaivaṃ saṃśrayet pradhānanṛpam/
GS41tikaniku:125: TY_7.16cd/.balasiddhiḥ saumyaphalair balibhiḥ krūrair jayo yuddhe//E16
GS41tikaniku:128: TY_8.2ab/.udito yato yataś ca bhramaṇe yadvārabheṣu cāragate/
GS41tikaniku:130: TY_8.3ab/.na pratiśukre siddhiṃ svalpo 'py arthaḥ prayāti yātṛṇām/
GS41tikaniku:131: TY_8.3cd/.kāmaṃ vrajet pratibhṛguṃ jijīviṣur nāstage śukre//
GS41tikaniku:132: TY_8.4ab/.kaluṣi vapuṣi grahahate pratilome nīcage 'stage ca bhṛgau/
GS41tikaniku:133: TY_8.4cd/.balasaṃpanno 'pi nṛpo yātā śatror vaśaṃ yāti//
GS41tikaniku:139: TY_.add8.2a/.[nakṣatraṃ tithi(tha)yas tathaiva karaṇaṃ vāras tathā gocaraṃ
GS41tikaniku:141: TY_.add8.2c/.[ye cānye śakunādayo nigaditāḥ sarve 'pi te śobhanā
GS41tikaniku:148: TY_.add8.1ab/.[naur iva vikarṇadharā vi(lacuna)(dha)veda vadhūr vibhāskareva dyauḥ/
GS41tikaniku:153: TY_8.6ab/.yo 'pi patir diśi yasyāṃ tasmin tatsthe na tāṃ diśaṃ yāyāt/
GS41tikaniku:157: TY_9.2ab/.hutvānalaṃ namaskṛtya devatāḥ svasti vācya viprāṃś ca/
GS41tikaniku:158: TY_9.2cd/.dhyāyan digīśam avilambitaṃ vrajed bhūpatiḥ sumanāḥ//
GS41tikaniku:159: TY_9.3ab/.kāryavaśāt svayam agamaṃ bhūbhartuḥ kecid āhur ācāryāḥ/
GS41tikaniku:163: TY_9.5ab/.dakṣiṇapārśvaspandanam iṣṭaṃ hṛdayaṃ vihāya pṛṣṭhaṃ ca/
GS41tikaniku:164: TY_9.5cd/.manasaś cāgamaśuddhiḥ ślokaś cāyaṃ munibhir uktaḥ//
GS41tikaniku:166: TY_9.6cd/.ekataś ca mano yāti tad viśuddhaṃ jayāvaham//
GS41tikaniku:169: TY_9.7cd/.vaktreṇa vā spṛśati dakṣiṇam ātmapārśvaṃ yo 'śvaḥ sa bhartur acirāt pracinoti
GS41tikaniku:170: TY_9.8ab/.muhurmuhur mūtraśakṛt karoti na tāḍyamāno 'py anulomayāyī/
GS41tikaniku:171: TY_9.8cd/.akāryabhīto 'śruvilocanaś ca śivaṃ na bhartus turago 'bhidhatte//
GS41tikaniku:172: TY_9.9ab/.skhalitagatir akasmāt trastakarṇo 'tidīnaḥ śvasati mṛdu sudīrghaṃ nyastahastaḥ
GS41tikaniku:173: TY_9.9cd/.drutamukulitadṛṣṭiḥ svapnaśīlo vikomo bhayakṛd ahitabhakṣī naikaśo 'sṛkśakṛtkṛt//
GS41tikaniku:175: TY_9.10b/.yāyād yātrānulomaṃ tvaritapadagatir vaktram unnamya coccaiḥ/
GS41tikaniku:177: TY_9.10d/.tatkālaṃ vā madāptau jayakṛd atha radaṃ veṣṭayan dakṣiṇaṃ ca//
GS41tikaniku:184: TY_9.14ab/.svayam atha racitāny ayatnato vā yadi kathitāni bhavanti
GS41tikaniku:186: TY_9.14cd/.sa jayati sakalāṃ tato dharitrīṃ grahaṇadṛgālabhanaśrutair upāsya//
GS41tikaniku:194: TY_9.17cd/.svapneṣv api tāni śubhāśubhāni viḍlepanaṃ dhanyam//
GS41tikaniku:195: TY_9.18ab/.mṛdur anukūlaḥ snigdhapavanaḥ tadvad vīnā(ṇā)ś ca śasyante/
GS41tikaniku:196: TY_9.18cd/.lalāṭaṃ dhanur athendraṃ(nuraindraṃ)na śubhadam anyatra śastaṃ(sta)phalam//
GS41tikaniku:205: TY_9.23ab/.mṛgavihagā śasyante pradakṣiṇaṃ viṣamasaṃkhyayā ca mṛgāḥ/
GS41tikaniku:210: TY_9.25ab/.visrambhahā krodhavaśe(śo) nṛśaṃse(saḥ) kṣudrā(draḥ) pramādī na bahuśrutā(ta)ś
GS41tikaniku:213: TY_9.26ab/.ato viparyastaguṇena rājñā tādṛgvidho 'ris tv abhiyuktamātraḥ/
GS41tikaniku:214: TY_9.26cd/.tarur ghuṇair jagdha ivāttakāryo mahān api kṣipram upaiti
GS41tikaniku:219: TY_9.28ab/.saṃgrāme va(ya)m amara(dvija)prasādā(t) jyeṣyāmo ripubalam āśv
GS41tikaniku:225: TY_9.29cd/.yuddhasya yātrāsama eva kālaḥ kū(krū)reṣu lagneṣu ca kūṭāyudhaḥ(kūṭayuddhaṃ)//
GS41tikaniku:228: TY_9.30cd/.āgantunāśāya bahirmukhās te tulyaṃ vihaṅgaiḥ saramātmajau(jā)ś
GS41tikaniku:231: TY_9.31b/.sūryendvoḥ pariveṣakhaṇḍam athavā dṛśyeta yasyāṃ diśi/
GS41tikaniku:233: TY_9.31d/.sainye vāpi yato viśanti hi tataḥ śatro(troḥ) puraṃ ghātayet//
GS41tikaniku:234: TY_9.32ab/.pātālarkṣe rāhuketvo(tvoḥ) pure 'reto(s to)yocchittiḥ sālapātaś ca kāryaḥ/
GS41tikaniku:243: TY_9.34cd/.yuddhānte mṛgaśakunaiś ca dīptanādaiḥ no bhadraṃ bhavati jite
GS41tikaniku:248: TY_9.35c/.yad anyam a(da)pi vikṛtai(taṃ) na vijayāvasāne bhavet
GS41tikaniku:249: TY_9.35d/.tadā sukham akaṇṭakaṃ nṛpatir atti deśe ripuḥ(ripoḥ)//E35
